### 1) GET all artists (public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artists
Accept: application/json

###

### 2) GET one artist (public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/artists/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 3) POST create artist (ADMIN only - Basic Auth)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/artists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQ=

{
  "firstname": "Ada",
  "lastname": "Lovelace"
}

###

### 4) PUT update artist (ADMIN only - Basic Auth)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/artists/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQ=

{
  "firstname": "Updated",
  "lastname": "Artist"
}

###

### 5) DELETE artist (ADMIN only - Basic Auth)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/artists/1
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46cGFzc3dvcmQ=
